    {
      "id": "jkqew0gsaerxws2jua",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 1730,
      "width": 3200,
      "height": 170,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#4a4a4a",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 544562,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 121079,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Key principles\n\n- Firm side is the only paid surface; clients and collaborators are FREE and infinite (per pricing model).\n- Lifecycle gate (D-027): outbound WhatsApp/SMS only fires when project.lifecycle = 'published'. Draft sends are suppressed and logged.\n- Every cross-persona handoff is a WhatsApp event after publish - this is the distribution loop and the wedge.\n- Magic-link auth (short-TTL JWT) means collaborators and clients never sign up, never see a password.\n- Internal staff use a desktop-dense UI; external personas use mobile-first single-screen flows.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "fxg84x6ln5poznnxsk",
      "originalText": "Key principles\n\n- Firm side is the only paid surface; clients and collaborators are FREE and infinite (per pricing model).\n- Lifecycle gate (D-027): outbound WhatsApp/SMS only fires when project.lifecycle = 'published'. Draft sends are suppressed and logged.\n- Every cross-persona handoff is a WhatsApp event after publish - this is the distribution loop and the wedge.\n- Magic-link auth (short-TTL JWT) means collaborators and clients never sign up, never see a password.\n- Internal staff use a desktop-dense UI; external personas use mobile-first single-screen flows.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 12
    },
